{"tid":406278,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本推出可維持記憶力的香口膠","createTime":"2017-09-19T13:45:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-19T15:53:48.000Z","uid":13468,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"96f746a2691c7a7e1ab0712a7be078cd42580fa6","tid":406278,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T13:45:13.000Z","msg":"日本太狂了！ 推出可維持記憶力的口香糖<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2197116\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2197116&d=RwxKApIyLqjTLCqDI3HY%2BosQCuff2cTRbXvS6e969MQ%3D&h=cafdc866\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2197116&h=944aa64e\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2197116</a><br />\n<br />\n2017-09-18 17:07<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕一般人想到口香糖的功用，大多都是解嘴饞或紓壓，但日本樂天推出超狂口香糖，主打可維持記憶力，引發討論旋風。<br />\n<br />\n據《產經新聞》報導，這款口香糖具有保持記憶力的功能，而且為了讓老人家食用時感到安心，特別設計成不沾黏假牙。口香糖加入了銀杏葉的萃取物，也就是銀杏內酯與銀杏黃酮苷。這兩者都已經過證明，老人服用後能夠有效保持對數字與文字的記憶力。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpYD6ao1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpYD6ao1.jpg&h=3629c8dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n 日本樂天推出號稱可維持記憶力的口香糖。（圖擷自《產經新聞》）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpfLJU1k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpfLJU1k.jpg&h=fb7a11a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n 口香糖有兩種口味，不含稅價格在140日元左右（約新台幣38元）。（圖擷自《產經新聞》）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n口香糖已於9月5日上市，分成綠色與金色兩種外包裝，代表不同口味。綠色包裝為粒狀口香糖，帶有銀杏的溫和味道，共有12粒。金色包裝則是片狀口香糖，是屬於薄荷口味，一共有9片。不含稅價格約在140日元左右（約新台幣38元）。<br />\n<br />\n不過樂天也強調，本產品並不適用於診斷、治療、預防疾病等療效。也就是說這並非藥品，本身還是口香糖。"},{"pid":"b221fe33fe4acdc6121e6396d8b8d784f78861df","tid":406278,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T13:47:41.000Z","msg":"睇錯左持久力香口膠"},{"pid":"8b76ceadf6958dd7c7812c1ec0d49fc9aedf7801","tid":406278,"uid":7840,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T13:48:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"085a08075667cb8a30f005b20c92216c2dc932d1","tid":406278,"uid":19990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T15:05:07.000Z","msg":"叮噹法寶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e55d7b54fd5e32b9107c324aae4c4cac674bf901","tid":406278,"uid":13468,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T15:09:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://monthly.wealth.com.tw/files/3462743b75444ad691398835ad57fc89.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmonthly.wealth.com.tw%2Ffiles%2F3462743b75444ad691398835ad57fc89.jpg&h=68679daf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2d89887d8b0b2698feda229bde035fe32cafb094","tid":406278,"uid":84360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T15:25:37.000Z","msg":"睇錯以為係係記憶枕咁既香口膠 過一段時間就還原番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61c67222f24204e1ad1697534877b4444a58404a","tid":406278,"uid":11687,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T15:51:35.000Z","msg":"試左<br />\n隻味道好撚奇怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7026e89177bef95ed6b8db3415b91dd9b323ec64","tid":406278,"uid":14758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T15:53:48.000Z","msg":"本身就嚼都會幫助架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}